These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, havana, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, scooter
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, june
3 different pets are kept: pony, fish, goat
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, cottage
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, yellow
3 different games are played: canasta, domino, go
 1. the person playing canasta is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person playing go is the owner of the goat##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is between the person who likes yellow and the havana-smoker##2
 4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the owner of the fish is the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Cigar      | havana    | oliveros   | prince           |
| Transport          | subway       | scooter    | jet-ski         |
| Birthday         | january    | june  | july        |
| Pet           | pony | fish   | goat      |
| House   | ranch-style        | cottage    | gothic-revival       |
| Color   | aquamarine     | mauve  | yellow       |
| Game         | canasta     | domino | go |

