.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, taxi, van
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, april, august
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, dressmaker, writer
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, cooking, video-games
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dunhill, chaman
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, orange, brown
 1. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the bus##2
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is the fisherman##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the writer##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | bus   | van    | taxi         |
| Flower          | poppy    | daisy | bellflower          |
| Birthday   | march  | august  | april     |
| Job   | writer       | dressmaker      | fisherman         |
| Hobby   | video-games      | cooking   | magic-tricks    |
| Cigar           | game        | chaman      | dunhill         |
| Color         | orange | aquamarine  | brown |

