.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, van, bike
City: hannover, san-francisco, rome
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, december
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, software-developer, security-guard
House: cape-cod, art-deco, ranch-style
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, tea
 1. the person driving the van is the art-deco house##1
 2. the security-guard is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person who growslily is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is the art-deco house##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is between the software-developer and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 8. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the van##1
11. the software-developer is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Transport          | bike      | van      | ship      |
| City         | hannover   | rome | san-francisco |
| Flower   | lily | begonia    | zinnia          |
