City: liverpool, prague, colone
There 3 different types of food: pepper, cucumber, potato
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, snooker
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating potato##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person driving the scooter and the aristoff-smoker##2
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who likes grey##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in may##2
10. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
