There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, lavender, grey
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, old-henry
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, skydiving, camping
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, sunflower
 1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person who growslily is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who likes lavender##2
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the old-henry-smoker##2
 7. the person who growslily is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 8. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the palace house is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
10. the cape-cod house is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Birthday      | january          | august         | october      |
| Movie-Genre          | action     | mystery         | satire |
| House           | wooden | palace    | cape-cod   |
