6. the italian is the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
8. the person who likes blue is the blend-smoker##1
9. the person who likes amber is between the turkish and the person who's birthday is in march##2

.:: Answer ::.
