.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
House: modern, futuristic, ranch-style
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, havana, pall-mall
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey, emerald
There 3 different types of food: onion, avocado, cranberry
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, firefighter, scientist
3 different games are played: chess, domino, snooker
 1. the scientist is in the middle##1
 2. the futuristic house is in the middle##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person playing snooker is between the modern house and the person eating onion##2
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the doctor##1
 9. the person who likes grey is the person playing chess##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person playing chess is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
